attr.title: Humming Out
attr.desc: A casual 2D pixel platformer adventure game with puzzle elements. You find yourself in a dark cave surrounded by crystals and hostile creatures. As a small and fragile hummingbird, you need to avoid all obstacles and navigate your way out of mysterious places and through challenging puzzles.
attr.inst:
You can purchase Humming Out at: https://mfproject.itch.io/hummin-out 

Download the Linux version and extract it, and place the HumminOut.x86_64.pck file in the gamedata directory. This has been tested with the HumminOut_Linux.zip, Dec 04 2022 release.
